{
  "stem": "10588.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as they took her out, they took me in that she should see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I didn't know if she's still conscious or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I looked at her and just with her face she gave me sign not to tell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that moment, I couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why would she allow herself to be so beaten, and even maybe killed, to protect a stranger practically?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It- it was just an acquaintance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just knew who he is, because I went to school there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now, too, they take me in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She's going to let them beat me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't understand, may she forgive me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And but I knew that I have to-- that this is an important moment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wasn't completely dumb.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I understood-- started to realize that maybe she must have a good reason.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they took me in, and I was next in line in beating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From what I later found out what they beat my mother, though it was severe, was nothing in comparison how they beat her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I didn't say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I, too, was silent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I, too, would not betray somebody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because it's not menschlich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was my test, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I didn't say even after I was beaten.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they saw that neither my mother, even though she heard me screaming, she didn't tell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't tell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I heard one of them saying [SPEAKING GERMAN], that he doesn't believe that we know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they let us go home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I realized then that that was my mother's and my test of menschlichkeit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the first time I learned about spiritual resistance, that you don't have to take just a gun, that there's something else.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
